column2: "...Do you intend to continue tormenting her, you bastard?"
"Your mission to save everyone is a cursed mission, and you should be able to see the result."
"You should be able to see what will happen to she who bears warped darkness and sorrow, and vanished."
"Do you intend to repeat the past?"
"...No matter what you think, the result will never change."
"If you truly care for her, slay her, immediately."
